quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  11,108,"Ke bona abo basikelelekileyo baya kuba sePaladesi bahlale apho ixesha lonke eliya kunyanyezelwa ngamazulu nomhlaba, ngaphandle kokuba iNkosi yakho Ithandile, (eso iya kuba) sisipho esingenasiphelo"
  11,109,"Wena ke (Muhammad) ungabi nantandabuzo ngezinto ezinqulwa ngaba bantu. Akukho nto bayikhonzayo ngaphandle koko kwakukhonzwa ngooyise mandulo. Yaye inene, siza kubahlawula ngokupheleleyo umvuzo wabo ngaphandle kwesinciphiso"
  11,110,"Inene Sanika uMûsâ iNcwadi kodwa kwavela iyantlukwano apho kuyo, ukuba kwakungekho ngenxa yelizwi elalisele liphumile livela eNkosini yakho, umcimbi ngowusele wagwetywa phakathi kwabo, kananjalo inene bona baneentandabuzo kanobom ngayo (le ‘Kurân)"
  11,111,Kananjalo umntu ngamye kubo iNkosi yakho Iza kumhlawula imisebenzi yakhe ngokuzeleyo. Inene Yona Ikwazi konke oko bakwenzayo
  11,112,"Ke wena yima nkqo uqine njengoko uyalelwe ndawonye nabo (bangabafundi bakho) baguqukayo (babuyele kuAllâh), bangagabadeliyo batsibe imida, (ka-Allâh). Inene Yena Uyakubona oko nikwenzayo"
  11,113,"Ke wena ungatyekeli ngakwabo benza ubugwenxa, hleze uMlilo ukurhece, yaye akunabakhuseli ngaphandle koAllâh, ungayi kuncedwa nakuncedwa"
  11,114,Kananjalo wena yenza iSalâh ngazo zozibini iziphelo zemini nangeeyure ezithile zobusuku. Inene izenzo ezilungileyo ziyazisusa izenzo ezingcolileyo kwabo banenkathalo
  11,115,"Uze ube nomonde, inene, uAllâh akawulahli umvuzo wabenzi bokulungileyo"
  11,116,"Akwaba phambi kwenu kwakukho abantu ababenobulumko, bethintela abanye ukuba bangenzi ukungcola emhlabeni (Kodwa akuzanga kubekho namnye) ngaphandle kwabambalwa babo eSabasindisayo phakathi kwabo! Abo babengabenzi bobubi babeleqeka emva kolonwabo lwezinto eziyolisayo zobomi beli hlabathi baza baba zizingcoli"
  11,117,"Ke kaloku iNkosi yakho yayingekhe Isuke Itshabalalise izixeko ngobugwenxa, abantu bazo bengamalungisa"
  11,118,Ukanti ukuba iNkosi yakho Yayithandile ngeYayisuke Yabenza abantubabasisizweesinye. Kodwababengazukuyeka ukuphikisana
  11,119,"Ngaphandle kwalowo iNkosi yakho Imenzele iNceba yayo, kananjalo Yabadalela loo nto ke. Kananjalo iLizwi leNkosi yakho sele lizalisekisiwe, elithi: “Inene Mna Ndiya kuzalisa isiHogo ngeejinni nabantu ndaweninye”"
  11,120,"Ke kaloku konke oko Sikubalisela kona wena (Muhammad) kweendaba ezilungileyo zabaThunywa kungenxa yokuba Senzela ukuba intliziyo yakho yomelezeke iqine ngazo. Kananjalo ngaso esi (sahluko) kufike inyaniso kuwe, ndawonye nesilumkiso nenkumbuzo kwabakholwayo"
  11,121,"Yithi ke kwabo bangakholwayo: “Yenzani ngokwamandla enu, nathi ngokwethu siya kwenza (ngeyethu indlela)"
  11,122,Kananjalo lindani! Nathi oku kwethu silindile.”
  11,123,"Yaye kokuka-Allâh okungabonwayo emazulwini nasemhlabeni, kananjalo kukuYe apho yonke imicimbi ibuyela khona. Khonza Yena ke wena, ubeke ithemba lakho kuYe. iNkosi yakho Ayingaba Ayikwazi oko nikwenzayo"
  12,1,Alif-Lâm-Râ Ezi zivesi zeNcwadi ecacileyo (i’Kur’ân)
  12,2,Inene Siyithumele (emhlabeni) iyi’Kur’ân yesiArabhu khon’ukuze niqiqe
  12,3,"Thina (Muhammad) Sikubalisela awona mabali alungileyo ngesiTyhilelo seThu (esisityhile) kuwe, esiyile ‘Kur’ân. Ukanti ngaphambili kunoku wawungomnye wababengazi nto ngayo"
  12,4,"Ke kaloku uYûsuf wathi kutata wakhe: “Hini na tata! Inene mna ndibone iinkwenkwezi ezilishumi elinanye nelanga nenyanga ziqubuda kum.”"
  12,5,"(Uyise) wathi: “Hini na nyana wam, uze ungawubalisi umbono wakho kubantakwenu, hleze benze iyelenqe ngawe. Inene uShaytân, lutshaba oluselubala loluntu"
  12,6,"Ke kaloku (nyana wam) iNkosi Iza kukukhetha Ikufundise ukutolika amaphupha, Igqibelelise uBabalo lwaYo kuwe nakwinzala kaYa’kûb, njengoko Yalugqibelelisayo kooyihlo- mkhulu, uIbrâhîm, noIs-hâ’k mandulo! Inene iNkosi yakho, nguSolwazi, uSobulumko.”"